I'll create a new report based on these execution logs.

EXISTING STRUCTURES

### Iron Mining and Smelting Setup
- Iron ore chest at position containing 800 iron ore
- Multiple burner inserters positioned at:
  - One inserter at (-13.5, -51.5) to (-15.5, -51.5)
  - One inserter at (-14.5, -50.5) to (-14.5, -52.5)
- Iron furnace (status: NO_INGREDIENTS)

### Coal Mining Setup
- Coal mining drill (status: NO_FUEL)
- Coal storage chest containing 33 coal

ERROR TIPS

### Fuel Management Errors
- Ensure sufficient coal is available in inventory before attempting to insert fuel into entities
- Monitor fuel levels of mining drills regularly to prevent NO_FUEL status

### Resource Extraction Errors
- Multiple failed extraction attempts indicate either:
  - Target container is empty
  - Agent is not in correct position for extraction
  - Ensure proper positioning and resource availability before attempting extraction

### Entity Placement and Manipulation
- When placing and rotating inserters, verify the final orientation matches the intended input/output flow
- Ensure proper alignment between inserters and their target entities

NAMESPACE

Functions:
- insert_item(prototype, target, quantity): Inserts items into target entity
  - Success: When inventory has required items and target is valid
  - Failure: When insufficient items in inventory

Variables:
- coal_drill: EntityType (Mining Drill)
- iron_chest: EntityType (Chest)
- iron_furnace: EntityType (Furnace)
